      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "During gameplay you roll 2d12 against a target determined by your situation and your statistics. Actions and tasks are performed by rolling a check and comparing the result with your active score associated with the action or task; rolling under the active score results in a success."
        }
      ]
    },
    "c9e823a8-39b5-4e84-8ccb-bb9cfb2c81d0": {
      "id": "c9e823a8-39b5-4e84-8ccb-bb9cfb2c81d0",
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "You are trying to move stealthily to enter the courtyard of a facility without the guards spotting you. Your active score is 17, so you roll 2d12 and if you roll 1 to 17 you have do move stealthily enough to bypass the guards."
        }
      ]
    },
    "2aa66aa1-6a69-4e5c-af41-15f2929a2557": {
